events.title: F3 Muletown 4th Anniversary Convergence
events.headline: Celebrate four years of impact in Columbia, TN.

location.name: Riverwalk Park Basketball Court
location.address: 102 Riverside Dr, Columbia, TN 38401, United States
location.notes: Look for the basketball courts near the river. Plenty of parking on site.

events.summary: Join the F3 Muletown brotherhood for a special 60-minute bootcamp to mark four years of workouts, fellowship, and faith in Columbia.
highlights: Bootcamp-style convergence featuring Qs from across the region.
Spotlight on four years of F3 Muletown's growth and impact.
Coffeeteria on site with local partners and opportunities to bring FNGs.
